{"tid":1285084,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實林鄭係咪想救香港經濟","createTime":"2019-07-04T12:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T12:22:15.000Z","uid":62133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b32b42df9ac0aa738640c58d06a7d1c9cf328a1","tid":1285084,"uid":62133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"香港近年經濟差消費意欲低，<br />\n估唔到一個反送中個個又買水買口罩買頭盔買遮買保鮮紙<br />\n呢d野唔係因為反送中鬼有咁好生意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣搵香港人錢好過搵過大陸錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時樣樣野都老奉要免費，依家個個睇份報紙都幾十幾百蚊咁訂閱黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日睇到個po 仲要買歌買碟添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪有晒計劃咖<br />\n<br />\nBTW <br />\n屌你蘋果開多幾個plan 啦<br />\n得個3蚊點振興本港經濟呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c05567256de06aaaa31334dd4b408835777dbf","tid":1285084,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"291a722a2f755307c9d0a812e7cc94eb84b6e4f5","tid":1285084,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"九月俾月費咪得 咁急做咩"},{"pid":"93628e0a4fed4971465b327b28441107ea085b4f","tid":1285084,"uid":62133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"291a722a2f755307c9d0a812e7cc94eb84b6e4f5","tid":1285084,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"九月俾月費咪得 咁急做咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201